<![CDATA[<h1>在Niri+DMS环境上使用wallpaper engine壁纸</h1><p>作者：Pdch（pd.ch@qq.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="先决条件">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%85%88%e5%86%b3%e6%9d%a1%e4%bb%b6"></a>
先决条件
</h2><p>首先需要配置好如下内容。</p>
<h3 id="niridms环境">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#niridms%e7%8e%af%e5%a2%83"></a>
Niri+DMS环境
</h3><p>这个在<a href="https://github.com/AvengeMedia/DankMaterialShell#installation">DankMaterialShell</a>的readme中一行命令就可以安装了。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="cl">curl -fsSL https://install.danklinux.com <span class="p">|</span> sh
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="wallpaper-engine">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#wallpaper-engine"></a>
wallpaper engine
</h3><p>老生常谈的壁纸软件，在steam上下载。</p>
<h3 id="linux-wallpaper-engine">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#linux-wallpaper-engine"></a>
linux wallpaper engine
</h3><p>我们只是使用wallpaper engine来搜索、下载、管理壁纸。要在Linux上使用则需要根据readme安装<a href="https://github.com/Almamu/linux-wallpaperengine">linux-wallpaperengine</a>。编译安装完成后需要在PATH中，例如如果在zshrc中添加路径则只会在zsh会话中生效，参考此<a href="https://github.com/sgtaziz/dms-wallpaperengine/issues/19#issuecomment-4187194612">issue</a>。</p>
        
